                </p>
              </section>
              <hr />
              <section class="special-thanks">
                <h2>Special Thanks</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://www.officinemattoli.it/"
                      >Officine Mattoli</a
                    >
                  </li>
                  <li>Lorenzo Raponi</li>
                  <li>Claudio Balboni</li>
                  <li>Alessandro Muscolini</li>
                </ul>
              </section>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img
                src="/img/caramella/Locandina_jpeg.jpg"
                alt="Cover Caramella Short Movie 2024"
              />
              <img
                src="/img/caramella/STILL_00.jpg"
                alt="STILL 0 Caramella Short Movie 2024"
              />
              <img
                src="/img/caramella/STILL_01.jpg"
                alt="STILL 1 Caramella Short Movie 2024"
              />
              <img
